C project skeleton
------------------

All what you need for proper project base.

Prerequisites
=============

All you need are these packages to compile and run properly:
	- cmake
	- build-essantial

Recommended optional packages:
	- python-yaml
	- doxygen

Installation
============

To build out-of-tree:
	$ mkdir build && cd build && cmake .. && make

To install it after being built:
	$ sudo make install/strip

To build a debian package:
	$ sudo make package

To build a source tarball:
	$ make package_source
EOF
